item.title: Need help with java
item.dc:creator: @x_spike_x x spike x
item.description:
@x_spike_x wrote:

Well make sure, the new jdk v6.0 hasn’t been out as long as you may think.

Go to:
http://java.sun.com/javase/downloads/index.jsp

Then nect to Jdk 6u1, click download.

Then accept the licence agreement, then select your format, e.g. windows. i would highly recommend online installers, so if your on windows, click “windows online installer”.

Then just save/download the file and go through the setup, then you have jdk 6

=================================
Hope this helped, if not, feel free to pm me.
